VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(int|short|unsigned)\s+\w+\s*=\s*\w+\s*\+\s*(\d{5,}|INT_MAX|UINT_MAX);
WHEN EXPR MISSING:INT_MAX|UINT_MAX|__builtin_add_overflow|SafeAdd|checked_add|overflow|bounds
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects arithmetic operations prone to overflow or wraparound.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Integer Overflow or Wraparound.
